------------------------------------------------------------ INSTALLATION

Tested Configurations:

   perl 5.004_04, 5.004_53-5.004_55


   Solaris 2.5.1

     SC4.0 18 Oct 1995 C++ 4.1 / ObjectStore 4.0.1+
     SC4.0 18 Oct 1995 C++ 4.1 / ObjectStore 5.0.*


   Digital Unix OSF1 V4.0 / AXP

     Dec C++ Compiler / ObjectStore 5.0

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

- ./t/zpeek.t is very sensitive to the success of the other tests.

- Keep running 'make test' until the database size matches.  It takes
me three trials.  If it will not match, there is a serious refcnt
problem.  Also see 'ossize -c'.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you succeed on a system that is not listed in above, please send
a note to perl-objectstore@parallax.co.uk announcing your success!

